metadata.title: Parents | Stand-up Comedy by Ravi Gupta
metadata.description:
I am touring in india with my Stand up comedy solo "Kal Ki Chinta Nahi karta" Click on the link below to book tickets -
https://in.bookmyshow.com/events/kal-ki-chinta-nahi-karta-ft-ravi-gupta/ET00329412

About the Video -
The journey of this set started back in April 2020 when I moved back to my native place in UP. In this video, I talk about my parents and How I actually got to know them on a whole new level in the past 2 years. They mean the world to me so this video has some bizarre and funny
